blog.description: hannah. 29. western mass.

summary: man....i was so ecstatic when i snagged my rep tickets last year..little did i know that the summer i was supposed to go my ex...
body: man….i was so ecstatic when i snagged my rep tickets last year..little did i know that the summer i was supposed to go my ex got sick and our relationship turned into an abusive one. at least a month before my tour date the cops started getting called, i started to get pushed around, and things ended pretty horrendously..i tried so hard to enjoy my show. i was pretty miserable up till tay came on stage and then i kinda felt better because her happiness made me happy. but, still, in the back of my mind i was still reeling from the awful couple of months i had. the breakup came two days before the show. honestly, worst timing ever. i wish i could say that i enjoyed the show to its full potential…but i just cant. I dont remember certain things about the show because i wasnt 100 percent there…ahhhhhh life.
